{"text_id":231650,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," emergence"," of"," quantum"," Hall"," ferro","magnetism"," in"," graphene",","," a"," phenomenon"," where"," spin","-","polarized"," electrons"," form"," a"," collective"," state"," of"," strong"," correlation","."," Recent"," experiments"," have"," observed"," such"," a"," state"," at"," high"," Landau"," level"," fillings",","," however",","," a"," complete"," theoretical"," understanding"," remains"," lacking","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," employ"," a"," SU","(","4",")"," boson","ization"," approach"," to"," analyze"," the"," interplay"," between"," graphene","'","s"," sub","lattice"," and"," spin"," degrees"," of"," freedom","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," inter","-","sub","lattice"," Coulomb"," interaction"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," driving"," the"," system"," towards"," ferro","magnetism","."," Our"," method"," allows"," us"," to"," capture"," the"," competition"," between"," the"," Coulomb"," and"," Ze","eman"," energies",","," which"," is"," essential"," for"," understanding"," the"," observed"," phase"," transitions","."," By"," self","-","con","sist","ently"," incorporating"," the"," Stoner"," instability"," and"," the"," Hart","ree","-","Fo","ck"," approximation",","," we"," reproduce"," the"," experimentally"," observed"," Landau"," level"," filling"," dependencies"," of"," the"," ferro","magnetic"," state","."," Our"," results"," provide"," a"," microscopic"," understanding"," of"," the"," quantum"," Hall"," ferro","magnetism"," in"," graphene",","," confirming"," the"," importance"," of"," SU","(","4",")"," symmetry"," in"," this"," system","."," This"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," ongoing"," efforts"," to"," unravel"," the"," rich"," phase"," diagram"," of"," graphene"," and"," its"," potential"," for"," applications"," in"," spin","-","based"," electronics","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}